Rebuilding the theme CSS takes a long time, do these are not built by default. Follow these steps to rebuild:

1. Remove the theme-*.css files from /assets/css
2. Move the .scss files you want to rebuild into /assets/css
3. Make any changes to the scss source
4. Build the site
5. Copy the _site/assets/css/theme-*.css to assets/css
6. Move assets/css/theme-*.scss back to /assets/css/_theme_source